Satu hari,

00:33:14.880 --> 00:33:16.070
ketika aku tidak punya apa-apa lagi

00:33:16.070 --> 00:33:17.400
tapi sepotong kain keras,

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:19.060
Aku tiba-tiba menemukan

00:33:19.090 --> 00:33:21.400
seekor Flame Crow muda di rumput.

